Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:02.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpa—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.09,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This may not be the right time to say it, but my name is Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I were to explain this situation simply, it would be like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:41.57,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}One month ago, I was found unconscious by Sumire-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:44.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and since then, I've been staying here as her pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:48.08,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bath time and meals are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.55,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But sex is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.85,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But recently, an old flame of my master's reappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how it is, so back to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:04.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:09.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That was…?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:10.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, my dog got excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.31,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,A dog? Oh yeah, you mentioned you had a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:20.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, and that pet is such a pet…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:23.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even at night, it's so noisy. And on top of that, vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really… and it's very unfriendly to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:26.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:31.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So, I'm sorry. Maybe you should…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:37.36,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But I want you to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:37.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:42.43,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Back then, I didn't want to say anything and leave you hanging because I was going overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.37,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,but now I can say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.10,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I want to…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:51.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, it is I who should say so…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:57.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:01:59.85,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.36,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want your dog to get jealous of me anymore, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.24,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:21.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This warm feeling is so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Gosh, Momo! Why were you spying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's not like I wanted to spy on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.27,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was just staying at home, obediently waiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,When I heard your footsteps,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:56.34,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I rushed towards the front door to greet you, and I saw that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,that unsightly kiss…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.88,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,He was even using his tongue! I didn't want to see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, really… even I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That senpai would suddenly do such a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.12,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really? You looked like you were pretty comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I have 20/20 vision in each eye. Isn't that impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.06,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,And I can even see your true feelings right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:19.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Right now, you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.10,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,"Now my mind is too preoccupied with my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't really have time to be chatting with Momo."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's what you're thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:29.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wha— What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? There's no way…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was so worried about your injury…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,70,,{\an8\i1}How did he figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,70,,{\an8\i1}It's true. I mean, the unrequited love\N{\i1}of 4 years ago has finally come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,70,,{\an8\i1}So I don't really have the right\N{\i1}state of mind to be thinking about other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:53.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,See? So I'll give you a bath. We have to wash your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,75,,{\i1}I guess I can cover it up by giving him a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,75,,{\i1}I'll have to keep him in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.44,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait… Momo, your bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's fine, I can do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What was that? He was the one who dropped my futons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.03,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hello…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello, Yuri-chan. Is this a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.20,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,No, it's not. Make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Today, at approximately 11 pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai saw me home after our first date, and he asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.31,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Umm, can't I listen to this tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, but Momo saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And he's kind of pouting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.22,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Throw him away. You have a boyfriend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:48.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But boyfriends and pets are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.36,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,But your pet is of the human species, and a male too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you for the prompt answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.60,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I knew all along…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:12.37,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Sumire-chan only regarded me as her old dog, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is it with Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,All the cigarettes I bought are gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why is this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.05,signs arno pro,text,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sumire-chan is STUPID!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:07.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, come down! Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:18.07,title,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,140)\blur0.7}You are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.07,episode,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,377)\blur0.6}3. Boyfriend vs. (male) pet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This morning I made him curry, but he wouldn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I went over and saw him feigning sleep, with his Noh-mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Plus, there were mini tomatoes placed in each of my commuting shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I accidentally crushed them…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.39,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What could be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:38.99,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.70,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your counseling session.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.70,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That's all right, she is not a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.30,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,There's a telephone call from the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.77,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, please tell him that I will call him back as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.84,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Isn't that the girl working at the coffeehouse on the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.55,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I scouted her because I needed an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:04.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.96,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,And, about your problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.72,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,it doesn't need counseling. You need a pet advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.43,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,True, I told you to come to the 14th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.16,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,but I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Today's schedule is full of appointments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:17.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:17.80,petto,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But you seem very close with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.84,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.01,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,it's just a business-like relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:38.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I felt like I was beginning to understand your feelings\Nabout bringing a pet along to No Man's Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,my dog was also there for me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,when I was going through difficult or depressing times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.17,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:55.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So, as I thought, I don't want to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.74,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,There's this train of thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:03.78,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,what modern women need is not a lifelong spouse, but a lifelong friendship with a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.12,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Think about it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:12.12,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Everyday, there are various things that frustrate you, giving you stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.96,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Society, your job, your superior, your subordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:22.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,allergies, the phone that doesn't ring, your happy-looking girl friends, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.57,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Not everything in this world is on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.47,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, not even the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:34.54,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,When you think that the person you love is healing your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.75,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,it's just a happy misjudgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:44.25,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Long ago, women would work hard for men, for their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.29,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,There was a time when that was considered to be good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.29,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,But that time has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:54.36,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You don't want to feel stress from other people when you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:59.73,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,But being alone is lonely. For that, they are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.14,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:09.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think I understand that point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My pet always accepts me unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.85,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Right? You will probably be single for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:20.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.89,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You've become addicted to your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.39,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,A very convenient roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.03,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:33.17,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,When we men hear that a single working woman has a pet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.40,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,this is what we think:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.44,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,"Oh, it's over for that woman."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,They're going to be single for the rest of their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:44.45,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,and they're trying to use a pet to fill the place of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:50.55,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I mean that's a lifestyle, too…\NWhat am I saying? That is also…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.29,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,That'll be enough, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.19,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I have more to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I will never come to the 14th floor again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.96,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Your pet is a male, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.50,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to love your pet too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.67,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,He is, after all, only a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.30,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,He may serve as family, but he's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.01,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Please do not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My pet is a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That is something I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:25.45,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Umm, I couldn't help but overhear…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.22,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Something similar happened with my dog, Goma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.49,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,He did various mischievous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:32.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.72,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.90,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,He would purposely poop on my clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.90,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,and gnaw on my favorite furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:44.11,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I heard that when their master's attention shifts elsewhere, they'll feel very uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.81,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,So at times like that, it's better to treat them gently rather than scold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.22,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,He's really cute. Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:00.66,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Its eyes are like mine and its ears are also very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're the one who's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:07.70,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey, you really haven't gotten laid? With your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.53,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That again? It's getting annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.00,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,But she's an incredible woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.50,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Really? She's expressionless, and don't you think she's too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.64,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey, but don't you feel like you want to? Living together and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:22.58,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, if you're asking whether I want to or not, it would be a lie to say I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.48,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But if you're asking, wouldn't you have to in order for the relationship to begin, that's not how it is either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.05,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.29,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But that kissy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.92,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want your dog to get jealous of me anymore, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.32,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Why would I be jealous, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.76,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan bathes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.16,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I get to zip up the back of her dress, and even get to see her bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.50,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I even get to see her in pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.37,petto overlap,Junpei,0,0,0,,Everyone's watching! Calm down, Takeshi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.54,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I am calm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.37,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm naturally a cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.64,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,But in any case, it's only two more months, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.24,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.98,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You said you were going to try out for the upcoming performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:55.88,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.65,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Geez, where did your cool go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.02,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,So deep down you're jealous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.45,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Maybe I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.52,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,… as a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.10,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.10,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.70,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I see you've found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.51,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I see you've found me out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.17,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Why are you holding that trash bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.98,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.25,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,As you can see, I live here. At Sensei's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.01,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.55,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I told you guys to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.10,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Are you living with that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.29,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:48.53,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're trying to do, but if you try to mess up my life now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.17,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Better to be gentle than to scold them…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Masa Saito's final battle got taped over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, I know you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I won't get mad, so please come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hey, Momo! I'll give you a bath, so come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll give you treatment and a scalp massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,After that, I'll clean out your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:18.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please, Momo, stop being mad at me. You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.39,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.66,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't go out with anyone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I thought so too, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:33.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That as long as I had my job and a pet, it would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So just because I have a boyfriend doesn't mean I'm going to kick you out all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You can stay—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.94,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,If you really want to…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll let you wash my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Gosh, you silly boy! Don't make me worry like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That hurts, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.26,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Mmm… it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Today, I was given a new special article project to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:14.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's kind of like a big job. Seems like the animal costume article was a big success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.95,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Wow, that's good. That's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, where were you before you came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.35,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.49,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I got into a fight with my parents and left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.69,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been learning classical ballet since I was two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I've even been trained overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:39.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I never grew any taller and was never able to get the role of a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.71,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,In modern dance, there are all sorts of dance moves and it doesn't matter if I'm short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:50.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There's a lot of variety, so it's interesting too. But my parents were against it, so I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:00.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The moment you stand on the stage, the atmosphere and the feeling you get;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,no matter how many times I do it, I still get goose bumps from the joy I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.63,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But this is nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I love getting shampoos from Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Just wait a second, stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.92,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:33.12,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The Brazilian president suddenly decided to come to Japan and I've been running around with the other reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You seem pretty busy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:41.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And I was wondering…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.77,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Will I be able to see you the day after tomorrow, before my night duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all right. I have that day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.11,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Actually, I bought something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's the Dog Language Interpreting Device that was so popular last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.34,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Dog language?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.81,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yup! Actually, I like dogs a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.48,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Back in my hometown, I have two at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.28,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Right now, I live in an apartment where pets aren't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,my appartment doesn't allow it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.99,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,So, can I come visit it, your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.18,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,My brother's pet, Mirumiru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.28,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Mirumiru-chan's getting so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.21,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,This is the towel he always uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.18,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Apparently, if you lay him here, he'll calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm sorry I asked for such a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:41.19,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Really! I don't know why I have to help you protect your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:44.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really! I don't want to be protected by this old lady either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:44.86,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.93,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to throw away this pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't fight, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But Sumire-chan, you're the weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.77,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Bringing a dog in to replace me, and trying to cover things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:56.60,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.64,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're a Tokyo University graduate, yet you could only come up with such childish tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't help it. I couldn't think of any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I finished cleaning the front and the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.08,petto overlap,Yuri,0,0,0,,I heard that you can distinguish pets by their smell, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.50,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Even my sweat has a floral fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's almost time, so can you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.69,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan, you're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:15.52,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. When visiting someone, it's common courtesy to arrive five minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, go for it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He'll be going home at night, so don't pout like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:30.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I won't pout. My master's happiness is my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,All lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.52,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh… I… came a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.99,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Were you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…\NNo… umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go home, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.37,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Come on, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.60,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.60,petto overlap,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.84,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,See you later, Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Bye, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:08.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wait, you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.31,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.69,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.42,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I think your mind is just playing tricks, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.49,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I have to go to my study school. Thanks for having us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Give your dog, Momo-chan, my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.60,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I guess it's just my mind playing tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:33.67,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that. My childhood friend suddenly decided to drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.84,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, I should apologize. I came too early myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The landlord let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The landlord…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:44.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh! That's the dog, Momo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.65,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.70,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Where do you intend to go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just hang around the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.78,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,She's not the same woman I saw last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.38,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Did I make a mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.88,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Shimizu-san from No. 106!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.89,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:23.89,petto overlap,landlord,0,0,0,,The weeds are growing so fast this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.55,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,As soon as I pull out the ones on that side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.69,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I have to work on this side. Then it's this side, that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:32.96,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh! Is that sukiyaki? With tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.56,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,No, I use potofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.30,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:40.40,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,So actually, you truly value your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.77,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, of course. Since it's an honor that she's letting me stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.04,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're too modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:50.15,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, I have to match up to my rival, the golden retriever Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.31,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,The first Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't even get to have a picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:59.22,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Well, the first Momo was extraordinary. He was a purebred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:02.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You know, if you keep comparing with extraordinary people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.86,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I hear your child gets messed up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.86,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,But he died early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:16.80,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Around ten years old? Sumire thought it was her own fault and became so guilt-ridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.41,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,She was crying constantly. I think it happened during middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.61,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you're going to make her cry someday, then I'd rather you left her early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.02,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What are your feelings on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.12,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,She'll probably be fine. I'm not loved enough to get cried over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.20,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:40.30,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,if you push this here like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,"Hey, play with me more." is what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.17,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This is interesting. No wonder it won an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:56.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, Momo! Sorry, it doesn't know how to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.41,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Puppies are all like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.45,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,When I heard its bark the last time, I thought it was a bigger dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:02.45,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:07.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…\NSometimes it barks like an adult, this little puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:10.83,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But today, it's not at all vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.13,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wonder if it has taken a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.73,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:16.73,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow, he's full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.31,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,He has a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm so sorry! Please change out of it. I'll wash it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll put a T-shirt right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:44.76,note,text,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obrigado{\i0} means {\i1}Thank you{\i0} in Portuguese.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so unaffected whenever Momo's naked, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It'll be dry soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:01.44,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:20.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Since it's before your night duty, I guess coffee would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:21.73,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:32.14,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Momo's sound asleep after running around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:42.98,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.39,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Time goes by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:47.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry things got a little panicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.98,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I can be with you like this, even for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:22.59,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Until just a while ago, you were on the other side of the earth and I couldn't even reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.61,0:24:40.21,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:42.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello, thank you for letting me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:43.85,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:52.12,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,What a pleasant young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:54.49,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What a hypocritical old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:25:00.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I mean, don't you think his smile is too pleasant? It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:02.63,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,I see your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.50,0:25:06.67,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,But you have a pretty nice face yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:09.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.44,0:25:11.74,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,For real, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.18,0:25:16.64,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks, I feel really good now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.64,0:25:18.78,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Really? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:22.25,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Wait a second…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.52,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Which floor is he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.12,0:25:30.13,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.39,0:25:32.96,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yay! I have Sumire-chan all to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.40,0:25:38.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:41.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Didn't you guys have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.33,0:25:43.24,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.01,0:25:46.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.71,0:25:48.98,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.88,0:25:51.61,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That sounds shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.75,0:25:55.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, I haven't done anything like that. It was just… unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.48,0:25:59.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you want for dinner? I'll make you anything you want tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.12,0:26:01.72,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Awesome! Omelette rice, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.52,0:26:05.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Gotcha. I'll go do some grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.19,0:26:07.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.50,0:26:11.37,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work, my replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:14.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:16.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,why was this thrown away?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.04,0:26:19.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.17,0:26:22.34,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The bristles were bent and I thought it would be a good time to replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.51,0:26:25.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a new one, what color would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.21,0:26:26.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.22,0:26:28.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But you can't use that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.42,0:26:36.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.16,0:26:38.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.33,0:26:41.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Expired, huh? Well, I guess everything has an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.03,0:26:45.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.27,0:26:46.57,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't want omelette after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.34,0:26:50.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You can just make do with what you have, just don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.87,0:26:53.74,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.98,0:27:00.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,All right. I won't go anywhere today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.47,0:27:23.71,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,As I thought, you write pretty good articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.71,0:27:29.74,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Successfully covering the costumes article and then a serious article afterward;
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.74,0:27:31.58,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,it's not something just anyone can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:36.38,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,For me, the part where Kumango-kun shook hands with the children made me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.02,0:27:39.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was also given a very valuable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.32,0:27:43.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:45.66,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,We're counting on you from now on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:47.86,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,But don't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.06,0:27:51.23,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,What decides your true worth is the next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:53.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.54,0:27:55.74,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.94,0:28:00.34,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, Hasumi-kun is here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:08.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:09.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Do you have time today?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.05,0:28:12.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes. The general meeting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.39,0:28:14.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.06,0:28:17.53,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,As I thought, those two are seeing each other after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:20.10,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kuraki-chan's rumors were correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.63,0:28:25.93,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, that "cool and beauty" can only be fished by someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:30.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.67,0:29:00.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone at work already knows about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:03.34,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Fukushima-san also asked me about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.44,0:29:04.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukushima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.84,0:29:07.68,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She said, "You two aren't going out by any chance, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.88,0:29:12.81,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,So, since that day, I've been telling people that we're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.58,0:29:16.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What an honest man…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:18.52,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Was that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.29,0:29:20.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.52,0:29:24.26,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,At the 7th block, there's a Mediterranean restaurant run by an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.26,0:29:26.49,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's not a very big restaurant, but would you like to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.93,0:29:28.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.10,0:29:31.20,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:31.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.58,0:29:42.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}People turn their heads at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:50.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I'm with this man, I don't have to care about my height or educational background.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.99,0:30:00.83,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,They're so picture perfect that it pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:06.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.20,0:30:10.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh? The lights are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.94,0:30:16.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.98,0:30:19.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.48,0:30:21.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.73,0:30:34.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, are you not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.15,0:30:51.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,A picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.98,0:30:54.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.76,0:31:08.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.65,0:31:35.21,note,text,0,0,0,,To Sumire-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.13,0:31:40.96,petto,,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.10,0:31:41.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:43.00,petto,,0,0,0,,You're in charge of the medical story, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:44.16,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.23,0:31:46.53,petto,,0,0,0,,Regarding this portion, we've discussed within our department,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.53,0:31:48.94,petto,,0,0,0,,should we change "neurons" to the Japanese word for neurons, to go with the rest of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.80,0:31:51.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, shall we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.07,0:31:52.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll make the corrections.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.94,0:31:54.21,petto,,0,0,0,,Thank you, that'd be a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.27,0:32:18.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.08,0:32:37.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that he might be lying somewhere unconscious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.59,0:32:39.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And hungry…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.15,0:32:40.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:42.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He mentioned the last time that he got some money from his performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.89,0:32:44.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,so he was going to buy milk on his own to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.73,0:32:45.59,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.76,0:32:49.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then maybe he was involved in an accident. Or in a hit-and-run and left dead in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.86,0:32:52.10,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you think about it logically, I doubt that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.10,0:32:53.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.37,0:32:57.44,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yes! He's a normal young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.44,0:33:00.64,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Just because he's missing a day or two doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.64,0:33:03.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.18,0:33:04.45,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.65,0:33:07.28,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Pets have their own pet lives too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.35,0:33:10.22,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Be happy that you have some of your free life back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What if he found a new master?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.96,0:33:17.66,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You have a new man yourself! A really good catch, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.53,0:33:22.80,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,That guy is only a pet, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.70,0:33:25.63,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,He is only a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.24,0:33:29.30,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,He may serve as family, but he's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:35.31,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.31,0:33:37.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is Iwaya from Tokyo Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.48,0:33:41.22,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya-san. Is this about your pet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.48,0:33:43.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.62,0:33:46.09,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I don't have time, so let's make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.69,0:33:50.39,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,A pet is a very useful source for healing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.39,0:33:51.76,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,They should also be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:58.20,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,But recently, there have been many masters who treat them as their own lovers or children.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.47,0:34:00.40,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That's very dangerous in several ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.90,0:34:03.20,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,A pet is a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.04,0:34:06.37,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,If you go beyond that boundary and deepen your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:09.94,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,your personal life will become unstable and your pet will also suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.71,0:34:13.60,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That's how it is. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.29,0:34:27.56,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.66,0:34:28.73,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Bon appetit!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.19,0:34:55.02,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,My Carlos disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.02,0:34:56.29,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.29,0:34:59.89,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,He has been gone for three days now. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.40,0:35:02.06,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,It's what they call pet loss, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.63,0:35:04.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Kuraki-san, what kind of cat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:06.97,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Huh, it's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.97,0:35:07.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.54,0:35:10.54,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That you would worry about my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.54,0:35:13.84,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,You think so? She's always leaving early to take care of her own dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.98,0:35:15.98,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.18,0:35:18.38,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, if you pass out so many flyers, I'm sure it will be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.38,0:35:20.22,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,You used the company copy machine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:23.05,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,It's okay! Don't be stingy, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.62,0:35:25.52,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll be useful to distribute them in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.61,0:35:27.28,note,text,0,0,0,,Has curly hair and is good at dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.28,0:35:28.68,note,text,0,0,0,,Momo (male)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.43,0:35:33.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.60,0:35:35.40,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard of that practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.40,0:35:38.30,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,At your front door, you leave your pet's favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.30,0:35:43.51,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Under the dish you place a piece of paper that says: "Waiting. Come home."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.51,0:35:44.77,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,And then your pet will come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.84,0:35:45.81,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.81,0:35:46.61,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,It's a superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.61,0:35:48.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I live in an apartment…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.53,0:36:04.39,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.27,0:36:13.64,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Does it hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.31,0:36:15.80,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.51,0:36:20.68,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,might get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.84,0:36:23.45,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:54.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He just rolled into my place like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.54,0:36:56.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.68,0:36:58.98,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.68,0:37:04.19,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back! You're early! What's for dinner tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.49,0:37:06.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He was so quick to adapt to this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.56,0:37:09.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and he disappeared so easily too?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.17,0:37:24.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.08,0:37:30.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Was everything a dream until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.58,0:37:48.40,note,text,0,0,0,,Dance Company 21
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.95,0:38:09.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm looking for someone. Do you know a Goda Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.59,0:38:12.19,petto,man,0,0,0,,Are you a fan of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.52,0:38:16.80,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You're Takeshi's…?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.80,0:38:17.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.20,0:38:19.86,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh… umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.00,0:38:22.36,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,He doesn't come here anymore, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.97,0:38:25.60,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Takeshi's acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:26.63,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.77,0:38:28.44,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You came during the last performance too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:35.31,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Takeshi is no longer a member of our dance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.31,0:38:38.65,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Previously, he came in as a guest performer because I asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.31,0:38:40.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.12,0:38:44.79,petto,man,0,0,0,,Sometimes, Takeshi is also a "rental prince" in classical performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.80,0:38:45.80,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Opera position.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.85,0:38:51.76,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,He's from a ballet school, so he has the talent to join any famous ballet company.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.86,0:38:52.79,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Opera position…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.70,0:38:57.57,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,But I wonder if it's really that much of a handicap to be short in classical dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:38:58.70,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,And…?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.90,0:39:01.00,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,What do you want from Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.00,0:39:01.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.10,0:39:04.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, umm. I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.60,0:39:06.11,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Like she's something to Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.61,0:39:10.81,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I'm asking, are you Takeshi's girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.91,0:39:11.91,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey, Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.91,0:39:14.55,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's over between me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.02,0:39:18.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.59,0:39:22.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm a reporter, for Tokyo Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:25.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I saw the performance the other day and\NI wanted to ask Goda-san some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.09,0:39:29.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I'll try somewhere else. I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.54,0:39:39.57,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.78,0:39:45.21,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You are pretty big…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.28,0:39:47.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.15,0:39:52.15,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I think Takeshi will go back to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.16,0:39:58.63,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Since he moved out of his house, he has never stayed at one place longer than a week, until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.03,0:40:01.46,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,So, I just feel that he'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.53,0:40:08.07,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.34,0:40:10.67,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,That Takeshi has gone on that audition trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.94,0:40:14.98,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Well, if he hasn't told her himself, wouldn't it be weird if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.44,0:40:16.88,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Plus, I don't know her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.89,0:40:35.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I gave up looking for him. It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.16,0:40:41.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,We were together every day, yet I don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.27,0:40:44.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But, I'm lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.17,0:40:45.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,… without Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.01,0:40:50.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't even remember what life was like without Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.25,0:40:53.48,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:41:01.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes. This time, it's my turn to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:06.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I decided to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.50,0:41:09.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So that Momo can come back at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.07,0:41:11.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,with his favorite food ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.77,0:41:17.07,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.00,0:41:45.43,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Sumire-chan, I will be gone for about two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.87,0:41:47.67,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.41,0:41:58.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I come back with sad eyes, don't ask any questions and just pat my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.89,0:42:07.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I come home smiling…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.59,0:42:11.96,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}well, in that case, just pat my head too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.37,0:42:18.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.17,0:42:20.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.20,0:42:25.57,petto,man,0,0,0,,The screening has finished, please stand up on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.18,0:42:37.79,petto,man,0,0,0,,Please take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:45.06,petto,man,0,0,0,,Finalists of the International Contemporary Dance Auditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:46.86,petto,man,0,0,0,,thank you for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.56,0:42:47.86,petto overlap,man,0,0,0,,As usual, they beat around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.40,0:42:52.87,petto,man,0,0,0,,You have the confidence to go to Germany, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.64,0:42:58.81,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.58,0:43:14.65,note,text,0,0,0,,{\an9}Waiting. Come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.91,0:43:40.98,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.36,0:43:48.52,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.39,0:44:56.42,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.93,0:45:05.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay if it's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.61,0:45:14.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I want to be with Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.19,0:45:25.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.41,0:45:48.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh no…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.74,0:45:51.71,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't think I can stop.
